text: Ikumi Nishibori (Japanese: 西堀育実, born 20 August 1981) is a Japanese female volleyball player. She played for the Japan women's national volleyball team, at the 2001 FIVB Women's World Grand Champions Cup. On club level she played for the Pioneer Red Wings. == References == == External links == * * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese women's volleyball players Category:Pioneer Red Wings players
